<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0f172a;
            --text-color: #cbd5e1;
            --accent-color: #38bdf8;
            --card-bg: #1e293b;
        }
        body {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: var(--accent-color);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        section {
            margin: 3rem 0;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #fff;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--card-bg);
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1rem;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
        .card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #334155;
        }
        .card h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        a {
            color: var(--accent-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Hello, I'm [Your Name]</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Web Developer & Tech Enthusiast</p>
            <p>Welcome to my personal corner of the internet. I build clean, functional, and user-friendly web projects.</p>
        </header>

        <section id="about">
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <p>I am passionate about learning new technologies, writing clean code, and solving real-world problems. Currently focusing on mastering frontend development and exploring cloud hosting environments.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="projects">
            <h2>My Projects</h2>
            <div class="grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Project One</h3>
                    <p>A brief description of a cool web application or tool you built. Built using HTML, CSS, and JS.</p>
                    <a href="#">View Code →</a>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Project Two</h3>
                    <p>Another project showcasing your skills. You can link this directly to its live demo or GitHub repository.</p>
                    <a href="#">View Code →</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="contact">
            <h2>Connect With Me</h2>
            <p>Feel free to reach out if you want to collaborate on a project or just say hi!</p>
            <div class="links">
                <a href="https://github.com[your-username]">GitHub</a>
                <a href="mailto:your-email@example.com">Email</a>
                <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
